data.description: Welcome home to this renovated,  cozy  3-Bedroom, 1 bath Ranch Home, on a half acre lot.   A delightful ranch-style home with a very convenient location near both downtown Marietta and Downtown Smyrna. One of the standout features of this property is its expansive, fenced flat backyard, a canvas for garden enthusiasts, or those envisioning a serene outdoor oasis.  The house boasts a brand-new septic tank,  new field lines, new water heater, new windows and newer HVAC offering homeowners peace of mind.  For the entertainers and relaxation-seekers alike, the outdoor shed is not to be missed. Not just any storage space, it's been transformed into a chic bar area, ready for weekend gatherings around the fire pit.  Don't miss out on the chance to own this prime piece of Marietta real estate. Schedule your tour today!
